testcase.name: Step3-case2: Replicator should retry until acknowledged by secondary
Step4-case1: Secondary should not acknowledge snapshots until persisted
Step4-case2: Secondary should retry persistence in every 100 milliseconds
Step5-case1: Primary does not acknowledge updates which have not been persisted
Step5-case2: Primary retries persistence every 100 milliseconds
Step5-case3: Primary generates failure after 1 second if persistence fails
Step5-case4: Primary generates failure after 1 second if global acknowledgement fails
Step5-case5: Primary acknowledges only after persistence and global acknowledgement
Step6-case1: Primary must start replication to new replicas
Step6-case2: Primary must stop replication to removed replicas and stop Replicator
Step6-case3: Primary must stop replication to removed replicas and waive their outstanding acknowledgements
